data.description: Welcome to your charming retreat in Burley's most enchanting neighborhood! Nestled amidst tree-lined streets, this brick beauty embodies the warmth of Thanksgiving gatherings. Step into the expansive living room, where memories unfold against the backdrop of updated flooring and a modern kitchen. With 5 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this home seamlessly combines comfort and style. The fully fenced backyard invites you to relax in privacy. Your dream home awaits—where every day feels like a holiday. Welcome home!
